messages.text: omg I am so hungoverrrrr
From last night?
Yeah. I ended up going to the soccer party after all
The one at Christian's house?
Yeah, how'd you know?
Casey...I was there...
You were???
Uh yeah
No way! I didn't see you!
You did see me...
Huh, really? Did I say hello?
What do you mean? We're best friends, of course you said hello. You were also downing some tequila.
Oh god that explains the hangover
You really don't remember me being there?
I don't....that's so weird...maybe I didn't recognize you or something...
I have been away all summer...but I don't think I look THAT different
Well, since you WERE there, maybe you can help me.
Help you?
Last night, I had a Cinderella moment.
I don't think puking on yourself qualifies as a "cinderella moment"
That explains the stain...
So what was your "Cinderella moment"?
Well, maybe less Cinderella, more Prince Charming. As in I am Prince Charming.
I met someone.
Yeah you met a lot of people. You're a very friendly drunk.
No, no, like a guy! A really nice guy...
Oh yeah?
He was so sweet, and cute, and he talked to me like he just knew me.
Maybe he did know you.
No I'm positive I had never met this dude in my life
Casey, you were preeeetty drunk.
Trust me, this was different.
Okay, so that's it? He just talked to you?
I'm not finished with the story! So we're talking for a while, and then he takes my hand...
Casey...
And then he looks at me with these crazy blue eyes...
Blue?
Well i think they were blue, idk i can’t remember. But he says, "I've never said this to anyone before, but I love you."
And then he kissed me!!!!
You sure his eyes were blue?
BEN I don't know, but that's not the point of the story! I had the most magical kiss last night!
So what's the Cinderella part of it?
I HAVE NO IDEA WHO HE IS
What?
Yeah! Someone called him, and he said he had to go. So I asked for his number and he said "you already have it"
Maybe you do...
Ben, I have no idea who this guy is! Why would I have his number?
I don't know. You clearly have no idea what color his eyes are, so who's to say you haven't met him before?
What's that supposed to mean?
It's just that if you had this "magical" moment with someone, wouldn't you remember the color of their eyes?
FOCUS BEN. I need your help.
MY help?
You were at the party last night. Maybe you know him! Or someone else who knows him!
Casey...
He's tall, on the skinny side, super tan, with wavy black hair and BLUE eyes
Casey, I think you dreamt up this guy or something
No way. He's real, and he's definitely my soul mate or something.
Thought you didn't believe in soul mates.
Ugh will you just help me?
yeah I'll help you. But on one condition.
YES YES YES
When you find out who it is, you can't freak out.
Why would I do that?
Just say you won't.
I won't.
Do you promise?
Pinky swear!!
Okay I'll ask Christian. He probably knows.
Hey man
Sup brah? Heard about you and Casey last night! :D
Yeah, so, I'm in a bit of a pickle
She sober up and friendzone you?
No, worse. She thinks we're soul mates.
WHAAAAT. Wait, how is that worse?
She doesn't know it was me...
Come again?
She was so drunk last night, she didn't recognize me, and now she thinks she had this “magical” moment with some random guy.
Oh shit
And now she wants me to find out who he is and set them up.
Well, you told her right?
Dude. You can't let her go on thinking that...you have to tell her!
I know! But how?
Just text her. Tell her, "hey remember that dude you made out with? That was me"
Yeah because that's gonna win her over. I'm just afraid it'll be awkward and ruin everything.
Better than not telling her right?
I guess.
btw, you coming over later?
Maybe. Depends on how things with Casey go.
Well, if you do, bring some advil. my headache is KILLER.
Plus I need help cleaning my house before the rents get home.
On second thought, I don’t think I can come over…
Come on ben!!!! PLEASE
BEN BEN I think I found him
What?
THE GUY. His name is Kurt
What the hell are you talking about?
Kristina said she talked to Melanie who met a guy named Kurt with black hair. But his eyes were brown...I was super off
Casey, it wasn't some guy named Kurt. I met that guy...he has a unibrow
Oh...
I have to tell you something. And I don't know how you're going to react.
Okay...
First of all, the guy you kissed? He has green eyes.
GREEN!! That's what they were! I remember now! Like sea glass
Wait, how'd you know they were green? Do you know him??
Kind of...
Well who is he???
Casey, it was me.
...what?
It was me. I kissed you.
But...I would've recognized you...
I lost a lot of weight over the summer, and I got tan.
I don't understand.
I love you Casey. I have for a really really long time. I just never had the guts to tell you until last night. I needed a little liquid courage.
That was you? You're sure?
Haha yes I'm sure.
I don't know what to say. You're my best friend.
I know. And if you want to forget it ever happened, I completely understand.
Wait what? I don't want to forget it happened
Really?
Of course. This means you’re my Cinderella.
oh please don't get mushy on me
GET OVER IT BEN. I'm coming over to your house. Right now.
Right now???
I'm hungover and I look like shit, but dammit, I'm gonna kiss you.
At least eat a breath mint okay? :)
You got it :)
